    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation at a lower price point. The exterior shows some age with noticeable scratches on the rear bumper and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some fading from the sun, though it remains intact and functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but it will likely need a new set of tires and a routine brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a dependable workhorse that has been used regularly, and while it isn't a showpiece, it gets the job done.",
      "price": 21500.0,
